    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanus</persName> Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >princeps</rs>. Cum principalis excellentia petitioni dilecti sui
                        clementer favet, igitur notum sit omnibus fidelibus nostris presentibus et
                        absentibus nos, quem ad hoc divina gratia promovit in principem ut
                        ecclesiarum defensor atque ditator existam, pro salute anime <rs
                            key="#parentOf">patris</rs> mei <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName>
                        ac <rs key="#parentOf">matris</rs> mee <persName key="#parentOf"
                            ref="#people/3003">Fredesinde</persName>, mei etiam et <rs
                            key="#marriage">uxoris</rs> mee <persName key="#Intercessory #marriage"
                            ref="#people/3011">Gaytelgrime</persName> et <rs key="#heirTo"
                            >heredum</rs> meorum, prudentia ipsius mee coniugis <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">interveniente</rs> et <persName key="#Intercessory"
                            ref="#people/4211">Goffridi Ridelli</persName>, <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Forests #Fisheries #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Churches #Aldius #Slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3060">Sancti Rufi</orgName> constructam in <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuana</placeName>, que nobis
                        concessa est a nostris <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelibus</rs> Capuanis et per
                        sacramentum firmata, cum omnibus pertinentiis suis intus Capuam et foras,
                        qualiter antiquitus pertinuit prefate ecclesie quovis modo et qualiter
                        tenuit et dominatus fuit <persName key="#Chaplain" ref="#people/4212"
                            >Herluinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chaplain">cappellanus</rs> noster, cum <rs key="#Slave">servis et
                            ancillis</rs>, cum <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">curtisanis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Aldius">aldiis</rs>, cum <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fish">piscationibus</rs>, cum <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">pascuis</rs>,
                        cum <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs> et universis
                        pertinentiis suis, dedisse, concessisse et confirmasse <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> constructa in <placeName ref="#places/109">Monte
                            Casino</placeName> per hoc principale scriptum et domno <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/2421">Desiderio</persName>
                        eiusdem monasterii <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> cunctisque successoribus, nemine prefato
                        monasterio domnoque abbati et suis successorum ex prescripta concessione
                        aliquam contrariam vel molestiam ingerentem. Quod siquis huius nostri
                        precepti violator extiterit, <rs key="#Penalty">mille libras auri obtimi
                        </rs>componat, medietatem nostre camere et medietatem predicto monasterio,
                        et domno abati cunctisque suis successoribus et, soluta pena, hoc preceptum
                        firmum et inviolabile maneat in perpetuum. Et ut firmus credatur et
                        diligentius observetur, manus nostra propria subscripsimus et nostri sigilli
                        inpressione sigillari precepimus. Signum domni Iordani <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">IORDANIS</persName>. Ex iussione prefate serenissime
                        potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer" ref="#people/3005"
                            >Cansolinus</persName> in anno principatus ipsius vicesimo quinto et
                        vicesimo anno <rs key="#Marquis/duke #Marca/ducatum">ducatus</rs> eius
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2343"><geogName
                                key="#Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/3001"
                            >Gaiete</geogName></placeName>. Data octabo kalendas Octubris, anno ab
                        incarnatione Domini nostri Iesu Christi .M. octoagesimo secundo. Scriptum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capue</placeName> per sextam
                        indictionem. </ab>
